	dprr:hasNoteText "In the consilium of L. Cornelius Lentulus Crus (218). Cos. 49, in Asia in 49 (Joseph. AJ 14.229, 238), probably as a Leg., lieut., as he is listed first after T. Ampius Balbus (J. Suolahti, Arctos 2, 1958, 152-163; cf. MRR 2.266).\n" .
